dataIdInfo.idAbs:
This toolset contains two tools. Please see detailed metadata of these tools.

  • Classify Bathymetric High Features: This tool classifies each bathymetric high feature into one of several feature types.

  • Calssify Bathymetric Low Features: This tool classifies each bathymetric low feature into one of several feature types.

searchKeys.keyword: This toolset contains tools for the classification of bathymetric high or low features.
